# Coze API Integration Rules
- Base URL: https://api.coze.com
- Authentication: Must use 'Authorization: Bearer <Personal_Access_Token>' in headers.
- Request Header: Must include 'Content-Type: application/json'.
- Common Body Structure: 
  - Chat endpoint: /v3/chat
  - Parameters: {"bot_id": "string", "user_id": "string", "stream": true, "additional_messages": []}
- Always check the latest field names (e.g., 'query' vs 'content') based on the Coze v3 API.
